# <type>(<scope>): <short, imperative description>
#
# Types: feat, fix, chore, style, refactor, test, docs, perf
# Scope: optional, e.g. deadline, plus, worker, ui, copy
# Body (optional): what & why, not how. Wrap at 72 chars.
#
# Examples:
#   feat(deadline): add swipe-to-complete gesture
#   fix(worker): validate license key format before KV lookup
#   chore(icons): generate PNG variants for PWA manifest
